    "createdBy": "kd795pd2q713d3q8q22z5d4a7s822ec0",
    "description": "Provider contract: any CLI that outputs {\"token\": \"...\", \"expires_at\": \"...\"} and exits 0 is a valid provider. Non-zero exit codes must be defined: stderr becomes error message. Provider config format is TOML with [commands] section for mint/refresh/revoke.",
