    "createdBy": "kd795pd2q713d3q8q22z5d4a7s822ec0",
    "description": "noscope mint outputs a scoped token to stdout for the caller to deliver however they choose (SSH, k8s secret, API call, etc.). noscope revoke explicitly revokes a previously minted token. These primitives decouple credential lifecycle from local subprocess management.",
